既問題 因為我可能都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n8月1號12點前截人龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (夠一定數會寄左先)  <br />\n我估10日內可以到你手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43dc2a740db911d5c3cd0e3701d417c007ce83cd","tid":340282,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T18:56:56.000Z","msg":"想問條線有咩特別？<br />\n認真問<br />\n兩個月用爛左三條iphone線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家呢條用膠紙痴住吊命"},{"pid":"52e0a59f7059a91814848b8390af1091c763f86a","tid":340282,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問條線有咩特別？<br />\n認真問<br />\n兩個月用爛左三條iphone線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家呢條用膠紙痴住吊命</blockquote><br />\n其實我都係狂爛IPHONE線<br />\n所以諗住大家一齊做下白老鼠<br />\n睇日本仔既貨係咪呃貨幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91ef6fe6f252c2d37e4d15f177c4c8f673da0e9e","tid":340282,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:11:00.000Z","msg":"原來已經3點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9269b82a2babb5db264f1f2658bc651573237025","tid":340282,"uid":60145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:12:40.000Z","msg":"買條xpower 有MFI 又唔爛  搞咁多野做咩"},{"pid":"04e01a0e373e007ef92447842c3c96c51ce53883","tid":340282,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:13:32.000Z","msg":"不如買xpower<br />\n本土牌子有保養<br />\n見身邊ip fd都用佢地<br />\n自己an機都買左條type c"},{"pid":"f4f5901a98281dfc2f0943195c34aaac475675ac","tid":340282,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T19:14:12.000Z","msg":"順豐到付15蚊阿大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6710f5f0b05